        <h2>Optical Image Stabilisation</h2>
        <p>
          Optical Image Stabilisation (OIS) started shipping in international smartphones in 2012 and analysts predict the market size to be 370 million units in 2017. OIS is widely recognised as the feature providing the most substantial improvement to smartphone camera quality in recent years. CML has already achieved success implementing this technology into a number of products, with the goal to ensure that the technology is integrated into every smartphone in the near future.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-2 gemini_image"></div>
    </div>
